me.lucko.helper.maven

Annotation Type MavenLibrary


  • @Documented
 @Repeatable(value=MavenLibraries.class)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MavenLibrary
    Annotation to indicate a required library for a class.
